    <string name="the_rules">
        <b>How to play:</b> \n \n
        Enjoy this two player dice game. \n \n
        Each player takes turns to play 13 rounds. \n \n
        The object is to get the highest number of points after all rounds have been played. \n \n
        To start a round the player rolls the dice up to three times. \n \n
        Press of any of the dice to hold them before rolling again. \n \n
        On each round the player must select a game category. \n \n
        Each game category will be worth a different number of points depending on the final roll of the dice. \n \n
        Press on each of the category buttons to see what the value of the turn is. \n \n
        Once happy with your selection, press the submit button. \n \n
        Pass to your friend who can play their turn.
    </string>


